      "text": "10. Eval & Feedback Loop\nPin dataset version, run evals, compare metrics across versions\nAuto-generate datasheet per version\nFeed winning filters and transforms back into new manifests",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "10. Eval & Feedback Loop\nPin dataset version, run evals, compare metrics across versions\nAuto-generate datasheet per version\nFeed winning filters and transforms back into new manifests",
